node.text:
Enjoy this 30 minute all-levels flow brought to you by @thebalancedbachelorette 🧘‍♀️ 

TBB provides everything you’ll need for a relaxing yoga class right to your hotel or Airbnb. All classes can be tailored to meet the needs and requests of your group. Hangover, or lack thereof 😉 

Heading to Scottsdale for your BACH? You can book a class with them on the BACH app!

node.text:
POV: You’re living your best life with your best friends, celebrating your BACH party, on a yacht in Cabo 🍹 (talk about GOALS @kasia_mazi) ❤️

As we get closer to spooky season in the states, here are some ways to get the MOST out of Fall BACH parties:

🛥 Head to places like Cancun, Cabo, Scottsdale, Austin, or Miami where the weather is much better in fall than it is in the peak of summer

🎃 Lean into spooky season and have some fall themed festivities (think wine tasting, picnics, and movie nights)

📲 Download the BACH app to plan your perfect party

#bacheloretteparties #cabobachelorette #fallbachelorette #bridetobe #engaged #maidofhonor #destinationparty

node.text:
🎉 $500 GIVEAWAY 🎉 That's right—we’re giving away $500 in BACH Bucks to one lucky party to use for any experience in the BACH app! From party buses to private chefs to bouncy castles to cabana boys, the BACH app has everything you've dreamed of for the perfect bachelorette weekend.

Here’s all you have to do to enter:

1️⃣ Like this post
2️⃣ Tag your besties in the comments
3️⃣ Enter using the swipe up link in our Instagram Story
⭐ 20 BONUS points if you have a party started in the BACH app! 💖 (enter the contest with the same email address you use for the BACH app)

Hurry! Enter by Monday, August 23rd. Winner will be selected at random and announced on August 24th. Good luck! 🎉

#girlsweekend #bacheloretteparty #bachelorettethemes #bachelorette #bacheloretteweekend #bridetobe #maidofhonor #gettingmarried
